-- European Union Has AAA Rating Affirmed by Fitch Ratings
-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 2012-03-29T14:48:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-29/european-union-has-aaa-rating-affirmed-by-fitch-ratings.html
The European Union had its AAA
long-term issuer default rating affirmed by Fitch Ratings, which
cited the support the EU gets from its 27 member states, nine of
which are rated AAA by Fitch.  The outlook is stable.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  